WEBVTT

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:02.576
or a police department
uses license plate detectors

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:06.496
to find out where
the officers' spouses are

00:11:06.520 --> 00:11:07.776
or those sorts of things,

00:11:07.800 --> 00:11:09.240
that is extremely dangerous.

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:12.976
But when a president repurposes the power

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:15.496
of federal surveillance
and the federal government

00:11:15.520 --> 00:11:18.576
to retaliate against political opposition,

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:19.800
that is a tyranny.

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:23.800
And so we are all activists now,

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:27.960
and we all have something
to fear from surveillance.

00:11:28.760 --> 00:11:32.536
